#: casca/help_content.py:39
msgid "Websites, turned into apps. No fuss."
msgstr "Des sites web transformés en applications. Sans complications."

#: casca/help_content.py:41
msgid ""
"Casca turns any address into a GNOME app: icon in the menu, its own window, "
"no leftover browser bar. This guide covers every option on the creation "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"Casca transforme n'importe quelle adresse en application GNOME : icône dans "
"le menu, fenêtre propre, sans barre de navigateur superflue. Ce guide couvre "
"chaque option de l'écran de création."

